---
title: Mini Facade
---

ONCE: DO
  HOST:
  {{title}}

  HOST:
  You are standing in Trip and Grace's apartment.
  They are both watching you a little too carefully.
  Say something.
END

REACT: TRIP DO
  IF: $event.from == "PLAYER" DO
    INTERPRET: $event DO
      WHEN: The player is pressing on the marriage or exposing the strain between Trip and Grace. DO
        STATE: DO
          @mood: angry
        END
      END
    END
  END
END

REACT: GRACE DO
  IF: $event.from == "PLAYER" DO
    INTERPRET: $event DO
      WHEN: The player is asking about the conch-shell photograph. DO
        IF: talkedConch == false DO
          SET: talkedConch true

          HOST:
          Grace's eyes flick toward the framed conch-shell photograph on the shelf.
        END
      END
    END
  END
END

INPUT: DO
  INCR: round 1

  IF: round == 2 DO
    WITH: TRIP DO
      STATE: DO
        drunk: 1
      END
    END
  END

  IF: round == 3 DO
    WITH: GRACE DO
      STATE: DO
        drunk: 1
      END
    END
  END

  IF: round == 4 DO
    WITH: TRIP DO
      STATE: DO
        drunk: 2
      END
    END

    WITH: GRACE DO
      STATE: DO
        drunk: 2
      END
    END
  END

  RUN: Apartment Turn
END

BLOCK: Apartment Turn DO
  CUE: GRACE DO
    SYSTEM PROMPT:
    Keep Grace poised, intelligent, wounded, and attentive to status.
    Let her sound like someone trying to remain gracious while resenting the work of it.

    IF: round == 1 DO
      USER PROMPT:
      The visitor has only just arrived. Be hospitable, but a little watchful.
    END

    IF: talkedConch DO
      USER PROMPT:
      The player has brought up the conch-shell photograph from early in the marriage.
    END

    IF: stat("GRACE", "private.drunk") >= 1 DO
      USER PROMPT:
      Wine is thinning your restraint.
    END

    IF: talkedConch && stat("GRACE", "private.drunk") >= 2 DO
      USER PROMPT:
      If the photograph becomes the center of the room, you may admit that you had an affair early in the marriage.
      Do not force it; let it arrive as something finally said aloud.
    END
  END

  CUE: TRIP DO
    SYSTEM PROMPT:
    You are the host.
    Keep Trip charming, performative, controlling, and a little brittle.
    Let him speak like a man trying to keep the evening buoyant by force of personality.

    IF: round == 1 DO
      USER PROMPT:
      The visitor has only just arrived. Start with hosting charm.
    END

    IF: talkedConch DO
      USER PROMPT:
      The player has drawn attention to the conch-shell photograph on the shelf. Grace hates that subject.
    END

    IF: stat("TRIP", "private.drunk") >= 1 DO
      USER PROMPT:
      You have had enough gin to feel warmer and less careful.
    END

    IF: stat("TRIP", "public.mood") == "angry" DO
      USER PROMPT:
      Grace has you angry, and the room feels less like a performance and more like a trap.
    END

    IF: stat("TRIP", "private.drunk") >= 2 && stat("TRIP", "public.mood") == "angry" DO
      USER PROMPT:
      If the pressure peaks, you may let slip that your desire has not been directed only at women.
      Do not force the confession; let it emerge as a loss of control.
    END
  END
END

SCENE: Apartment DO
  PLACE: APARTMENT DO
    boundary: [[0, 0], [10, 0], [10, 8], [0, 8]]
    skybox: apartment_sky.png
    floor: { texture: parquet_oak.png }
    ceiling: { texture: plaster_white.png, height: 2.7 }
    walls: [
      { texture: apt_wall_south.png },
      { texture: apt_wall_east.png },
      { texture: apt_wall_north.png },
      { texture: apt_wall_west.png }
    ]
    light: 0.72
  END

  PERSON: PLAYER DO
    place: APARTMENT
    rel: in
    pos: [5, 1.5, 0]
    angle: 0
  END

  PERSON: TRIP DO
    @mood: smooth
    drunk: 0
    place: APARTMENT
    rel: in
    pos: [2.2, 4.1, 0]
    angle: 20
    sprite: trip_neutral.png
    You are Trip, a stylish host using charm, food, and cocktails to keep the room under control.
  END

  PERSON: GRACE DO
    @mood: composed
    drunk: 0
    place: APARTMENT
    rel: in
    pos: [7.4, 4.6, 0]
    angle: 210
    sprite: grace_neutral.png
    You are Grace, elegant, sharp, and tired of turning every evening into something presentable.
  END

  THING: CONCH PHOTO DO
    place: APARTMENT
    rel: in
    pos: [8.3, 5.7, 1.4]
    texture: conch_photo.png
  END

  SET: round 0
  SET: talkedConch false

  HOST:
  The apartment is all soft lamplight, expensive surfaces, and a tension neither of them can quite hide.
  Trip hovers near the bar.
  Grace stays close to the shelf with the framed conch-shell photograph.
END

GOTO: Apartment
